  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Preparations are complete for\nthe Joint rally for good government\nto be held at Mantle park at 2\no'clock tomorrow afternoon by the\nfarmers and organized labor.\n\n\nIn addition to the speeches there\nwill be music and recitation by\nDorothy Mitchell, Spokane girl,\nwho will take the vaudeville stage\nnext week.\n\n\nAnother meeting Of the commit\ntee in charge Of the rally will be\nheld tonight at the Equal Suffrage\nclub rooms in the Hutton building."
    }
  ]
